languages.text: "Идем же, элантах. Оставим сие кладбище сомнений, несбывшихся надежд и обретенных страхов. Вместе".
"Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

languages.text: “走吧，外界人。离开这个满怀疑虑、失望与恐惧的坟冢，我们一起离开这里。”
languages.original_text: "Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

traits.locale_text: “走吧，外界人。离开这个满怀疑虑、失望与恐惧的坟冢，我们一起离开这里。”
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: «Vámonos, elantach. Abandonemos este cementerio de dudas, esperanzas rotas y nuevos temores. {mf|Juntos|Juntas}».
languages.original_text: "Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

traits.locale_text: «Vámonos, elantach. Abandonemos este cementerio de dudas, esperanzas rotas y nuevos temores. {mf|Juntos|Juntas}».
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: « Allons-y, elantach. Quittons ce cimetière peuplé de doutes, d'espoirs déçus et de peurs naissantes. Ensemble. »
languages.original_text: "Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

traits.locale_text: « Allons-y, elantach. Quittons ce cimetière peuplé de doutes, d'espoirs déçus et de peurs naissantes. Ensemble. »
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Gehen wir, Elantach. Verlassen wir diesen Friedhof der Zweifel, unerfüllten Hoffnungen und neuen Ängste. Gemeinsam."
languages.original_text: "Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

traits.locale_text: "Gehen wir, Elantach. Verlassen wir diesen Friedhof der Zweifel, unerfüllten Hoffnungen und neuen Ängste. Gemeinsam."
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: 「行こう、エランタ。この迷いの墓場、叶わぬ希望、そして新たな恐怖を捨て去ろう。共に」
languages.original_text: "Let us go, elantach. Let us leave this graveyard of doubts, unfulfilled hopes, and newfound fears. Together."

traits.locale_text: 「行こう、エランタ。この迷いの墓場、叶わぬ希望、そして新たな恐怖を捨て去ろう。共に」
traits.speaker: YrlietCompanion

languages.text: "Gidelim elantach. Şüphelerin, gerçekleşmeyen umutların ve yeni korkuların mezarlığından uzaklara gidelim. Birlikte."
